name: Unidentified Floating Obby
description:
What does UFO stand for?

Unidentified Floating Obby!

Obby is an Obstacle Course by the way, and you will be flying a spaceship today! 

Which is also unidentified... and one problem, it has no power. 

Right, well, good news... you can just push your little spaceship around and find some energy cubes lying around. 

You're going to need 12 energy cubes before you can head off with your buddies who are flying away right now. 

Wait, they're flying away. 

Crap.

Features
  • A speedrun timer. Become the very best, like no-one ever was.
Controls

The MOTHERSHIP has given you a file that came with the spaceship. It should be called "UFOControls.txt". If you did lose your file, you are screwed.

From developer: "UFOControls.txt comes with the zip file."

This game was made in under 72-48 hours, and was made for the game jam: Drawing Circle x Playmakers Jam, with the theme being UFOs.
